snippet.title: Best VGM 1226 - Phoenix Wright : Justice for All - Eccentric
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS, Wii
Phoenix Wright : Justice for All (2006)
Eccentric
Naoto Tanaka
